  "content_markdown": "1\n\n###  Application and Definitions\n\n1.1\n\nUnless otherwise stated, this Part applies to:\n\n  1. (1) a _UK Solvency II firm_ ;\n  2. (2) in accordance with [Insurance General Application 3](/pra-rules/insurance-general-application#2e5a9cd32e6d4026895a5d543b990108 \"Insurance General Application 3\"), the _Society_ , as modified by [5](/pra-rules/key-function-holder---notifications#84fb1e066aa64752a8d129c3d124cbd5 \"5\");\n  3. (3) in accordance with [Insurance General Application 3](/pra-rules/insurance-general-application#2e5a9cd32e6d4026895a5d543b990108 \"Insurance General Application 3\"), a _managing agent_ , as modified by [5](/pra-rules/key-function-holder---notifications#84fb1e066aa64752a8d129c3d124cbd5 \"5\");\n  4. (4) a _third country branch undertaking_ (other than a _Swiss general insurer_); and\n  5. (5) a _UK ISPV_.\n\n*Effective: 01/01/2016*\n\n1.2\n\nIn this Part, the following definitions shall apply:\n\n_key function holder notification form_\n\nmeans Form M.\n\n*Effective: 10/12/2018*\n\n2\n\n###  Key Function Holder Notification\n\n2.1\n\n[Deleted.]\n\n*Effective: 10/12/2018*\n\n2.2\n\nA _firm_ must provide the information required by [Insurance – Fitness and Propriety 4.1](/pra-rules/insurance---fitness-and-propriety#63445bf69a1e4ae9a2a8009469e4d2f5 \"Insurance – Fitness and Propriety 4.1\") for each _key function holder_ as soon as reasonably practicable after the appointment of the _key function holder_.\n\n*Effective: 01/01/2016*\n\n2.3\n\nThe _PRA_ directs that, subject to [2.4](/pra-rules/key-function-holder---notifications#6ae1f403e47148e5ab691be66f6c3e4a \"2.4\"), the information referred to in [2.2](/pra-rules/key-function-holder---notifications#ae5560f778244dd690fda57d3bc3398a \"2.2\") must be provided to the _PRA_ in the _key function holder notification form_ in accordance with [3.3](/pra-rules/key-function-holder---notifications#eb53a6be7f9943ed83e5d4f9848fb120 \"3.3\").\n\n*Effective: 01/01/2016*\n\n2.4\n\nThe _PRA_ directs that:\n\n  1. (1) where the _key function holder_ is to be approved by the _PRA_ to perform a _PRA senior management function_ , the _firm_ must provide the information referred to in [2.2](/pra-rules/key-function-holder---notifications#ae5560f778244dd690fda57d3bc3398a \"2.2\") to the _PRA_ in whichever Form is required for the _PRA senior management approval application_ , pursuant to [Insurance - Senior Managers Regime - Applications and Notifications 2](/pra-rules/insurance---senior-managers-regime---applications-and-notifications#cf386c0194624de5828a57391073f726 \"Senior Insurance Managers Regime - Applications and Notifications 2\"), which must be accompanied by a _statement of responsibilities form_ ; and\n  2. (2) where the _key function holder_ is to be approved by the _FCA_ to perform an _FCA controlled function_ , the _firm_ is not required to submit a _key function holder notification form_ to the _PRA_ to the extent the _firm_ provides the information referred to in [2.2](/pra-rules/key-function-holder---notifications#ae5560f778244dd690fda57d3bc3398a \"2.2\") to the _FCA_ as part of the application to the _FCA_ , with a _statement of responsibilities form_.\n\n*Effective: 10/12/2018*\n\n3\n\n###  Procedure for Making Applications and Notifications\n\n3.1\n\nThe _PRA_ directs that, save as required by [3.2](/pra-rules/key-function-holder---notifications#f292bb8cd11949ba90e42d403835ea26 \"3.2\") and [3.3](/pra-rules/key-function-holder---notifications#eb53a6be7f9943ed83e5d4f9848fb120 \"3.3\"), a _firm_ must make any applications, notifications or submissions required by this Part by submitting the form specified using the _ONA system_.\n\n*Effective: 01/01/2016*\n\n3.2\n\nIf, under any direction or rule in this Part:\n\n  1. (1) a _firm_ is required to make an application, notification or submission online; and\n  2. (2) the information technology systems used by the _PRA_ fail and online submission is unavailable for 24 hours or more,\n\nuntil such time as facilities for online submission are restored, a _firm_ must submit the specified form in the way set out in [Notifications 7](/pra-rules/notifications#8e186d20f3cf4d218117e0780f104f7c \"Notifications 7\").\n\n*Effective: 01/01/2016*\n\n3.3\n\nThe notifications required under [2.3](/pra-rules/key-function-holder---notifications#f3d7140772584b25991a988480470f2e \"2.3\") should be submitted in accordance with [Notifications 7](/pra-rules/notifications#8e186d20f3cf4d218117e0780f104f7c \"Notifications 7\").\n\n*Effective: 10/12/2018*\n\n4\n\n###  Forms\n\n4.1\n\nThe _key function holder notification form_ , Form M, may be found [here](https://www.bankofengland.co.uk/-/media/boe/files/prudential-regulation/authorisations/senior-managers-and-senior-insurance-managers-regimes-approvals/form-m-july-2018.pdf?la=en&hash=5C9E5D380C7A401A94BD584A2A43F55F99966230 \"Form M\").\n\n*Effective: 10/12/2018*\n\n5\n\n###  Lloyd’s\n\n5.1\n\nThis Part applies to the _Society_ and _managing agents_ separately.\n\n*Effective: 01/01/2016*\n\n6\n\n###  Transitional Arrangements for Key Function Holders (Deleted)",
  "content_html": "<div class=\"col9\">\n<div class=\"clear\"></div>\n\n\n<div class=\"part-content\">\n\n<div class=\"chapter-section\" data-version=\"f3b829896a61408abb69462fea305f8f\" id=\"d362482a655b46519c75926017df278c\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number rule-number--mega chapter-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t1\r\n\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<h3 class=\"header-sans chapter-heading\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\tApplication and Definitions\r\n\t\t\t\t</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"7bfd89580ae34383855d7b198397e7c0\" id=\"ad0506f05f134e6a8f64578ead7bfaf5\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"1\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t1.1\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>Unless otherwise stated, this Part applies to:</p>\n<ol class=\"new-bullet\">\n<li>(1) a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52930\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-0d29d447fd4b4fca868c1d2e5b5e2276\" title=\"UK Solvency II firm\">UK Solvency II firm</a></em>;</li>\n<li>(2) in accordance with <a data-mce-contenttype=\"5\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Chapter\" href=\"/pra-rules/insurance-general-application#2e5a9cd32e6d4026895a5d543b990108\" title=\"Insurance General Application 3\">Insurance General Application 3</a>, the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52231\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c757d61ac22a4f43b4565c1a14c53dfd\" title=\"Society\">Society</a></em>, as modified by <a data-mce-contenttype=\"5\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Chapter\" href=\"/pra-rules/key-function-holder---notifications#84fb1e066aa64752a8d129c3d124cbd5\" title=\"5\">5</a>;</li>\n<li>(3) in accordance with <a data-mce-contenttype=\"5\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Chapter\" href=\"/pra-rules/insurance-general-application#2e5a9cd32e6d4026895a5d543b990108\" title=\"Insurance General Application 3\">Insurance General Application 3</a>, a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52204\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-631b76adce9c4143ad8d33e593852c66\" title=\"managing agent\">managing agent</a></em>, as modified by <a data-mce-contenttype=\"5\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Chapter\" href=\"/pra-rules/key-function-holder---notifications#84fb1e066aa64752a8d129c3d124cbd5\" title=\"5\">5</a>;</li>\n<li>(4) a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52916\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8241961260a4c6394b7710d6bf24e03\" title=\"third country branch undertaking\">third country branch undertaking</a></em> (other than a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52910\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-7ecb61ce28ed4c4e947c300a772aa937\" title=\"Swiss general insurer\">Swiss general insurer</a></em>); and</li>\n<li>(5) a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52386\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-d657b35a131c4b4982032a800f337269\" title=\"UK ISPV\">UK ISPV</a></em>.</li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t01/01/2016\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"ebc0939c6b174d94a093754dfe1cbd54\" id=\"b66b86e87ae44da08c159c42446f4d12\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t1.2\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>In this Part, the following definitions shall apply:</p>\n<p><em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"67121\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-3eb075a3ccdf496e9738585a602c03dd\" title=\"key function holder notification form\">key function holder notification form</a></em></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">means Form M.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t10/12/2018\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\n<a class=\"list-links__link icon-previous\" href=\"/pra-rules/key-function-holder---notifications/15-02-2016#b66b86e87ae44da08c159c42446f4d12\">\r\n\t\t\tPast\r\n\t\t\t<span class=\"visually-hidden\">\r\n\t\t\t\tversion of 1.2 before 10/12/2018\r\n\t\t\t</span>\n</a>\n</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"page-utilities page-utilities--bg-grey\">\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"chapter-section\" data-version=\"6134ea2994394be9bfc4620bd28f801a\" id=\"0b9bba2377c542d1b90a571433e133b0\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number rule-number--mega chapter-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t2\r\n\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<h3 class=\"header-sans chapter-heading\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\tKey Function Holder Notification\r\n\t\t\t\t</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"cb6b1370c39a4c93b91be8dcec8cc2ab\" id=\"6ababeed0bf74f32892cac1cf02422fd\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"1\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t2.1\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>[Deleted.]</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t10/12/2018\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\n<a class=\"list-links__link icon-previous\" href=\"/pra-rules/key-function-holder---notifications/15-02-2016#6ababeed0bf74f32892cac1cf02422fd\">\r\n\t\t\tPast\r\n\t\t\t<span class=\"visually-hidden\">\r\n\t\t\t\tversion of 2.1 before 10/12/2018\r\n\t\t\t</span>\n</a>\n</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"532ebb6d76d648deb681c3976b91be22\" id=\"ae5560f778244dd690fda57d3bc3398a\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t2.2\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>A <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em> must provide the information required by <a data-mce-contenttype=\"7\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Rule\" href=\"/pra-rules/insurance---fitness-and-propriety#63445bf69a1e4ae9a2a8009469e4d2f5\" title=\"Insurance – Fitness and Propriety 4.1\">Insurance – Fitness and Propriety 4.1</a> for each <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52842\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-fd5d0277f5e14a8ea81a9cb3889733d4\" title=\"key function holder\">key function holder</a></em> as soon as reasonably practicable after the appointment of the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52842\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-fd5d0277f5e14a8ea81a9cb3889733d4\" title=\"key function holder\">key function holder</a></em>.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t01/01/2016\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"f1f6678f5b7f419bb17c11a74a177a6a\" id=\"f3d7140772584b25991a988480470f2e\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t2.3\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>The <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52117\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-494fbb81077e408f84519b8c66998fef\" title=\"PRA\">PRA</a></em> directs that, subject to <a data-mce-contenttype=\"7\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Rule\" href=\"/pra-rules/key-function-holder---notifications#6ae1f403e47148e5ab691be66f6c3e4a\" title=\"2.4\">2.4</a>, the information referred to in <a data-mce-contenttype=\"7\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Rule\" href=\"/pra-rules/key-function-holder---notifications#ae5560f778244dd690fda57d3bc3398a\" title=\"2.2\">2.2</a> must be provided to the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52117\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-494fbb81077e408f84519b8c66998fef\" title=\"PRA\">PRA</a></em> in the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"67121\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-3eb075a3ccdf496e9738585a602c03dd\" title=\"key function holder notification form\">key function holder notification form</a></em> in accordance with <a data-mce-contenttype=\"7\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Rule\" href=\"/pra-rules/key-function-holder---notifications#eb53a6be7f9943ed83e5d4f9848fb120\" title=\"3.3\">3.3</a>.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t01/01/2016\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"6184ddc9cfa94f63a28cab21cb41b638\" id=\"6ae1f403e47148e5ab691be66f6c3e4a\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t2.4\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>The <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52117\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-494fbb81077e408f84519b8c66998fef\" title=\"PRA\">PRA</a></em> directs that:</p>\n<ol class=\"new-bullet\">\n<li>(1) where the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52842\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-fd5d0277f5e14a8ea81a9cb3889733d4\" title=\"key function holder\">key function holder</a></em> is to be approved by the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52117\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-494fbb81077e408f84519b8c66998fef\" title=\"PRA\">PRA</a></em> to perform a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52568\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-1a0e61be7ef34efba8c7c001ca8c26d3\" title=\"PRA senior management function\">PRA senior management function</a></em>, the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em> must provide the information referred to in <a data-mce-contenttype=\"7\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Rule\" href=\"/pra-rules/key-function-holder---notifications#ae5560f778244dd690fda57d3bc3398a\" title=\"2.2\">2.2</a> to the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52117\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-494fbb81077e408f84519b8c66998fef\" title=\"PRA\">PRA</a></em> in whichever Form is required for the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"88189\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-037eda30748c4d3e96c59fd0d7048dc4\" title=\"PRA senior management approval application\">PRA senior management approval application</a></em>, pursuant to <a data-mce-contenttype=\"5\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Chapter\" href=\"/pra-rules/insurance---senior-managers-regime---applications-and-notifications#cf386c0194624de5828a57391073f726\" title=\"Senior Insurance Managers Regime - Applications and Notifications 2\">Insurance - Senior Managers Regime - Applications and Notifications 2</a>, which must be accompanied by a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"67123\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-d2efc30e1b394a7d8db2cdf03aa6afe3\" title=\"scope of responsibilities form\">statement of responsibilities form</a></em>; and</li>\n<li>(2) where the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52842\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-fd5d0277f5e14a8ea81a9cb3889733d4\" title=\"key function holder\">key function holder</a></em> is to be approved by the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52718\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-a6adfc5faca24b3186f3f7bee3c6db22\" title=\"FCA\">FCA</a></em> to perform an <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52565\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-4d084a65f6d6425f8b0dbef37e18160e\" title=\"FCA controlled function\">FCA controlled function</a></em>, the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em> is not required to submit a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"67121\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-3eb075a3ccdf496e9738585a602c03dd\" title=\"key function holder notification form\">key function holder notification form</a></em> to the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52117\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-494fbb81077e408f84519b8c66998fef\" title=\"PRA\">PRA</a></em> to the extent the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em> provides the information referred to in <a data-mce-contenttype=\"7\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Rule\" href=\"/pra-rules/key-function-holder---notifications#ae5560f778244dd690fda57d3bc3398a\" title=\"2.2\">2.2</a> to the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52718\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-a6adfc5faca24b3186f3f7bee3c6db22\" title=\"FCA\">FCA</a></em> as part of the application to the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52718\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-a6adfc5faca24b3186f3f7bee3c6db22\" title=\"FCA\">FCA</a></em>, with a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"67123\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-d2efc30e1b394a7d8db2cdf03aa6afe3\" title=\"scope of responsibilities form\">statement of responsibilities form</a></em>.</li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t10/12/2018\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\n<a class=\"list-links__link icon-previous\" href=\"/pra-rules/key-function-holder---notifications/01-01-2016#6ae1f403e47148e5ab691be66f6c3e4a\">\r\n\t\t\tPast\r\n\t\t\t<span class=\"visually-hidden\">\r\n\t\t\t\tversion of 2.4 before 10/12/2018\r\n\t\t\t</span>\n</a>\n</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"page-utilities page-utilities--bg-grey\">\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"chapter-section\" data-version=\"8d54e38075cd4ca2b87d871617765dc1\" id=\"7bccabfd084e410f85a2bf2e15b5e218\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number rule-number--mega chapter-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t3\r\n\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<h3 class=\"header-sans chapter-heading\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\tProcedure for Making Applications and Notifications\r\n\t\t\t\t</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"a75256e227ce4711bf96bcac2ff6a257\" id=\"c970f2b543594565a0c4f6b6ac331003\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t3.1\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>The <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52117\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-494fbb81077e408f84519b8c66998fef\" title=\"PRA\">PRA</a></em> directs that, save as required by <a data-mce-contenttype=\"7\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Rule\" href=\"/pra-rules/key-function-holder---notifications#f292bb8cd11949ba90e42d403835ea26\" title=\"3.2\">3.2</a> and <a data-mce-contenttype=\"7\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Rule\" href=\"/pra-rules/key-function-holder---notifications#eb53a6be7f9943ed83e5d4f9848fb120\" title=\"3.3\">3.3</a>, a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em> must make any applications, notifications or submissions required by this Part by submitting the form specified using the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52226\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-0432343f2aa34ff099752e8fb7688e22\" title=\"ONA system\">ONA system</a></em>.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t01/01/2016\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"534e2ecbabeb435ea8b65e90f0d8dcb5\" id=\"f292bb8cd11949ba90e42d403835ea26\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t3.2\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>If, under any direction or rule in this Part:</p>\n<ol class=\"new-bullet\">\n<li>(1) a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em> is required to make an application, notification or submission online; and</li>\n<li>(2) the information technology systems used by the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52117\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-494fbb81077e408f84519b8c66998fef\" title=\"PRA\">PRA</a></em> fail and online submission is unavailable for 24 hours or more,</li>\n</ol>\n<p>until such time as facilities for online submission are restored, a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em> must submit the specified form in the way set out in <a data-mce-contenttype=\"5\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Chapter\" href=\"/pra-rules/notifications#8e186d20f3cf4d218117e0780f104f7c\" title=\"Notifications 7\">Notifications 7</a>.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t01/01/2016\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"e1fd29dfecb548b497a729625fbd0258\" id=\"eb53a6be7f9943ed83e5d4f9848fb120\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t3.3\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>The notifications required under <a data-mce-contenttype=\"7\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Rule\" href=\"/pra-rules/key-function-holder---notifications#f3d7140772584b25991a988480470f2e\" title=\"2.3\">2.3</a> should be submitted in accordance with <a data-mce-contenttype=\"5\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Chapter\" href=\"/pra-rules/notifications#8e186d20f3cf4d218117e0780f104f7c\" title=\"Notifications 7\">Notifications 7</a>.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t10/12/2018\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\n<a class=\"list-links__link icon-previous\" href=\"/pra-rules/key-function-holder---notifications/01-01-2016#eb53a6be7f9943ed83e5d4f9848fb120\">\r\n\t\t\tPast\r\n\t\t\t<span class=\"visually-hidden\">\r\n\t\t\t\tversion of 3.3 before 10/12/2018\r\n\t\t\t</span>\n</a>\n</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"page-utilities page-utilities--bg-grey\">\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"chapter-section\" data-version=\"6c1f964bf7d24e46a881df5884677c39\" id=\"644cf07618b943b5a3f1bdbe2cffbf9a\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number rule-number--mega chapter-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t4\r\n\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<h3 class=\"header-sans chapter-heading\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\tForms\r\n\t\t\t\t</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"9336925ae1734e9d812c049e5a849f4a\" id=\"e94136baf1ae42f9a6b48819f92cc598\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t4.1\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>The <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"67121\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-3eb075a3ccdf496e9738585a602c03dd\" title=\"key function holder notification form\">key function holder notification form</a></em>, Form M, may be found <a class=\"external-link\" data-mce-description=\"Key function holder notification form\" data-mce-externalform=\"true\" data-mce-linktype=\"4\" href=\"https://www.bankofengland.co.uk/-/media/boe/files/prudential-regulation/authorisations/senior-managers-and-senior-insurance-managers-regimes-approvals/form-m-july-2018.pdf?la=en&amp;hash=5C9E5D380C7A401A94BD584A2A43F55F99966230\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Form M\">here</a>.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t10/12/2018\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\n<a class=\"list-links__link icon-previous\" href=\"/pra-rules/key-function-holder---notifications/01-01-2016#e94136baf1ae42f9a6b48819f92cc598\">\r\n\t\t\tPast\r\n\t\t\t<span class=\"visually-hidden\">\r\n\t\t\t\tversion of 4.1 before 10/12/2018\r\n\t\t\t</span>\n</a>\n</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"page-utilities page-utilities--bg-grey\">\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"chapter-section\" data-version=\"3b06f5b8d3ef4763b6e4118371d498f2\" id=\"84fb1e066aa64752a8d129c3d124cbd5\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number rule-number--mega chapter-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t5\r\n\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<h3 class=\"header-sans chapter-heading\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\tLloyd’s\r\n\t\t\t\t</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"d554f330956a4957b78bc9e233411e36\" id=\"1db3a7999c584f95877f6766584b4bcb\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"1\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t5.1\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>This Part applies to the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52231\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c757d61ac22a4f43b4565c1a14c53dfd\" title=\"Society\">Society</a></em> and <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52204\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-631b76adce9c4143ad8d33e593852c66\" title=\"managing agents\">managing agents</a></em> separately.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t01/01/2016\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"page-utilities page-utilities--bg-grey\">\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"chapter-section\" data-version=\"501c56a32de9476fa31596ee98bbfb64\" id=\"813e2119e1b14c868eb2e714e56fc935\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number rule-number--mega chapter-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t6\r\n\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<h3 class=\"header-sans chapter-heading\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\tTransitional Arrangements for Key Function Holders (Deleted)\r\n\t\t\t\t</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"page-utilities page-utilities--bg-grey\">\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div></div>\n</div>",
